{
  "stem": "1222.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I never talked before so much to the children about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't want to hurt them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I still don't want to hurt them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm keeping it to myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it's left a mark probably the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They're saying you helped your child when I was 12 years old that left my mark that I can't help it not to cry, because I hear the voice, like I said, for this crying for these hours in that grave.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that ditch where the children listen to me, what I showed them that I laid in that little ditch.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I would say, Archie knows better the measurement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It's probably no more than 20 feet from that grave, I was laying in that ditch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my children will tell you again-- and it was coming out from Israel, 18 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we made all these headstones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We signed it, all our names in English, some of them in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we put in like a Torah right in there, like in the Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it's a big, beautiful headstone, and the fenced in with steel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You know, they could break it with a fence, with a gate, with all the beautiful flags, and all the beautiful flowers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And now I hear that the government is planting trees all around there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Before, they [INAUDIBLE] throwing garbage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I feel that's the most wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I'm hoping in time that I'll go again saying the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And if the children will be in the mood to come, they will come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Could be danger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But I'll take my risks talking about that thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I feel my parents will pray to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
